        "title": {
          "en": "Hugging Face Unveils Gemma 4 for On-Device Multimodal AI",
          "zh": "Hugging Face 发布 Gemma 4：面向设备的多模态AI"
        },
        "tl_dr": {
          "en": "Hugging Face announced Gemma 4, a new model designed for frontier multimodal intelligence on devices.",
          "zh": "Hugging Face 发布了 Gemma 4，一款专为设备端前沿多模态智能设计的新模型。"
        },
        "key_takeaways": {
          "en": [
            "The newly introduced model is designated as Gemma 4.",
            "It is characterized by \"frontier multimodal intelligence.\"",
            "Its architecture supports \"on-device\" deployment."
          ],
          "zh": [
            "新推出的模型被命名为 Gemma 4。",
            "其特点是具备“前沿多模态智能”。",
            "该架构支持“设备端”部署。"
          ]
        },
        "impact": {
          "en": "The release of an on-device multimodal AI model could enable more applications to run locally, potentially reducing latency and increasing data privacy for users in various AI-powered scenarios.",
          "zh": "推出设备端多模态AI模型可能会使更多应用在本地运行，从而有望降低延迟并提高用户在各种AI驱动场景中的数据隐私。"
        },
        "source": "Hugging Face",
        "link": "https://huggingface.co/blog/gemma4"
      },
      {
        "title": {
