        "tl_dr": {
          "en": "Google DeepMind has released Gemma 4, open models designed for advanced reasoning and agentic workflows.",
          "zh": "谷歌DeepMind发布了Gemma 4，这是一组专为高级推理和智能代理工作流设计的开放模型。"
